232, 198.0882, 197.7767, 196.7878, 195.0351, 192.6809, 191.8236, 190.4527, 191.1458, 190.63, 191.0546, 191.6348, 191.1313, 191.557, 190.7378, 191.0995, 191.505, 191.2887, 191.0101, 190.9842, 192.8814, 192.2693, 191.4156, 190.7734, 190.3721, 191.0614, 189.9781, 190.4868, 191.1238, 189.8892, 189.831, 190.5951, 191.7163, 192.0384, 192.0082, 192.7932, 192.1109, 191.5387, 190.5221, 188.0901, 188.8725, 190.5492, 190.4403, 189.3051, 189.5501, 190.9272, 190.5877, 193.3894, 193.5776, 193.9598, 194.8823, 196.1211, 197.3203, 196.3962, 194.7661, 194.9042, 194.8467, 196.2582, 196.631, 196.7755, 196.4012, 196.5023, 195.0149, 195.7251, 194.7463, 193.391, 192.5457, 194.7839, 196.506, 194.5361, 194.1963, 195.2775, 192.7193, 196.1513, 196.1737, 195.704, 194.6229, 193.6181, 193.8158, 194.2588, 199.2328, 201.3118, 197.9373, 201.4982, 204.8449, 202.9979, 197.663, 198.7519, 202.2468, 199.1396, 197.1423, 199.283, 199.0696, 200.5925, 197.8149, 199.554, 201.4924, 200.1402, 198.6909, 201.4845, 208.7403, 210.5198, 210.9576, 212.7044, 214.9069, 213.9362, 215.5247, 214.7769, 215.3229, 212.2961, 212.7666, 212.8631, 211.2463, 208.098, 210.0973, 209.6045, 208.9051, 210.6798, 207.7952, 207.8808, 208.5313, 206.7807, 208.0475, 205.0339, 204.9568, 203.8201, 207.7643, 204.187, 204.9647, 204.0914, 205.3798, 206.749, 207.2547, 208.7762, 207.1069, 206.9283, 205.9309, 205.4866, 204.4941, 204.7693, 204.2408, 203.1961, 203.9958, 204.1967, 206.4662, 206.4368, 206.7268, 205.0266, 205.4906, 205.6217, 203.2875, 202.3039, 201.94], "summary_html": "<h1>中建投 逐鹿 Alpha 八大类日内因子 复现</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>研报构建 8 类、上千个日内分钟因子。复现实现每类最强 1 个 = 10 因子（含 1 类 2 选）+ 多个 composite 变体。原文 A 股 cross-section 最强。</p>\n<p>复现侧：10 因子全实现 + sign 在 commodity 域有 7 个翻转。最佳 <code>compt3_h7_ts</code> Sharpe <strong>1.100</strong> (kurt + lead_lag_corr + tail_vol_x_turnover 等权)。<strong>注意</strong>：fidelity reviewer 发现 7 个 flipped 因子中只有 1 个有正 Sharpe，real driver 是 <strong>kurt</strong> (paper-matching sign retained, single Sharpe 0.73)。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>1.05</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>4.7%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>4.4%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-6.2%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.08</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3057</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>1.23</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>0.9</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.03 / 1.41</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.43</span></td><td>0.69</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.17</span></td><td>0.71</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.26</span></td><td>0.63</td><td>1.68</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.92</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.16</span></td><td>0.63</td><td>1.52</td><td>0.37</td><td>0.56</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>high</code></td><td>最高价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>low</code></td><td>最低价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>volume</code></td><td>成交量</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>opi</code></td><td>持仓量</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 分钟级（聚合到日频输出）</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 6 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 6 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>76</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3058</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>87.8%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>46.9</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p>10 因子（每个 240 min 全日 window，21 day 滚动平均）：</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>因子</th><th>公式</th><th>sign (futures)</th></tr><tr><td>amplitude</td><td>max(high)/min(low)-1</td><td>-1 (paper)</td></tr><tr><td>mad_amp</td><td>mad(high)/last(close)</td><td>+1 (flipped)</td></tr><tr><td>upside_std</td><td>UpStd(close/close.shift(4)-1)</td><td>+1 (flipped)</td></tr><tr><td><strong>kurt</strong> (driver)</td><td>Kurt(close/close.shift(4)-1)</td><td>-1 (paper)</td></tr><tr><td>tail_volume_ratio</td><td>sum(vol[235:240])/sum(vol)</td><td>+1 (flipped)</td></tr><tr><td>tail_vol_x_turnover</td><td>F5 × sum(vol)/last(opi)</td><td>+1 (flipped)</td></tr><tr><td>lead_lag_corr</td><td>corr(high.shift(1), volume, 237)</td><td>+1 (flipped)</td></tr><tr><td>min_7min_ret</td><td>min(close/close.shift(7)-1)</td><td>-1 (flipped)</td></tr><tr><td>peak_count</td><td>Σ(close&gt;prev &amp; close&gt;next)</td><td>-1 (paper)</td></tr><tr><td>downside_std</td><td>DownStd(close/close.shift(3)-1)</td><td>+1 (flipped)</td></tr></table></div>\n<p>Composite (winner):</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{compt3} = \\frac{1}{3}\\big(z_{cs}(\\text{kurt}) + z_{cs}(\\text{lead\\_lag\\_corr}) + z_{cs}(\\text{tail\\_vol\\_x\\_turnover})\\big)</div>\n<p>仓位：cr_rank → rank_to_continuous → vol_target_scale(0.15) → rebalance_hold(7) → T+1。</p>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>R1 (Sharpe 0.726)</strong>: 10 因子 paper sign，发现 6 个负 Sharpe → 决定翻转。</li>\n<li><strong>R2 (Sharpe 0.916)</strong>: sign 翻转 + 3 composite + hold sweep → 提升 +26%。</li>\n<li><strong>R3 (Sharpe 1.100)</strong>: compt3 + compt5 + extended hold 网格 → 突破 1.10。</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>关键洞察</strong>： 1. <strong>kurt (峰度) 是 actual driver</strong>：paper sign retained, single Sharpe 0.73；其他 7 个 flipped 多数仍负 2. <strong>compt3 = kurt + 2 wash signals 起 diversification 作用</strong>，最终 Sharpe 1.10 是组合效应 3. <strong>hold=7 是 sweet spot</strong>，比 hold=21 (paper monthly) 更短</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>：minute (<code>comm_data/1min/kline_all.parquet</code>)</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>：80 商品期货</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>：7 day rebalance</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>：</li>\n</ul>  1. <strong>kurt 单因子驱动</strong>，组合 diversification 占比小\n<p>2. <strong>sign-flip 经验性</strong>而非理论性，可能过拟合 3. 与因子库 corr 0.18 (低，new signal) 4. compt5 (5 因子) 不如 compt3 (3 因子) — 加入弱因子拖累</p>\n<p><strong>结论</strong>：通过入库，但 caveats：kurt 是核心，可考虑单因子入库而非 compt3。</p>\n<h2>参数</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>默认</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td>intraday_window</td><td>240</td><td>全日分钟数</td></tr><tr><td>smoothing</td><td>21 day</td><td>滚动平均</td></tr><tr><td>hold_days</td><td>7</td><td>grid {1, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8, 9, 10, 12, 15, 21}</td></tr><tr><td>target_vol</td><td>0.15</td><td></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 0.9756</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 44.06s</li>\n</ul>"}